0method%2C%20the%20question%20is%20how%20much%20they%20will%20really%20be%20worth%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findustry%2Fauto%2Findia-used-electric-car-resale-market-battery-valuation-challenges-125102400824_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findustry%2Fauto%2Findia-used-electric-car-resale-market-battery-valuation-challenges-125102400824_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findustry%2Fauto%2Findia-used-electric-car-resale-market-battery-valuation-challenges-125102400824_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22My%20kids%20are%2014%20and%2015%2C%20and%20they're%20over%20trick-or-treating.%20I'm%20not.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222447%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author's%20two%20kids%20dressed%20as%20Darth%20Vader%20and%20a%20Stormtrooper%20on%20Halloween%20in%202016.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68f66b8a1c1f80efbec5e531%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221835%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20didn't%20realize%20how%20much%20she'd%20miss%20going%20trick-or-treating%20with%20her%20kids.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Kristina%20Wright%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMy%20two%20sons%2C%20now%2014%20and%2015%2C%20used%20to%20love%20trick-or-treating.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20didn't%20realize%20how%20much%20I%20loved%20going%20with%20them%20until%20they%20stopped%20wanting%20to%20go.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThis%20year%2C%20I'll%20be%20handing%20out%20candy%20on%20the%20front%20porch%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%2015%20years.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20saying%20%26quot%3BThe%20days%20are%20long%20but%20the%20years%20are%20short%26quot%3B%20is%20never%20truer%20than%20when%20I'm%20looking%20back%20at%20Halloweens%20past.%20Before%20I%20was%20a%20mom%2C%20I%20used%20to%20sit%20on%20the%20front%20porch%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-i-dont-hand-out-candy-on-halloween-food-bank-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehanding%20out%20candy%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20neighborhood%20kids%2C%20often%20alone%20because%20my%20Navy%20husband%20was%20away%20on%20deployment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20%26quot%3Booh%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bahh%26quot%3B%20over%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmost-popular-halloween-costumes-kids-adults-pets-nrf-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecute%20costumes%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20encourage%20the%20tired-looking%20parents%20to%20hang%20in%20there%20%E2%80%94%20as%20if%20I%20had%20any%20idea%20what%20it%20took%20to%20wrangle%20a%20toddler%20into%20an%20ill-fitting%20and%20itchy%20costume%20(one%20they%20wanted%20to%20wear!)%20or%20negotiate%20with%20a%20cranky%20preschooler%20who%20was%20up%20two%20hours%20past%20their%20bedtime%20as%20they%20bounced%20around%20the%20house%20in%20a%20sugar%20rush.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20I%20found%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222384%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author's%20husband%20trick-or-treating%20with%20one%20of%20their%20sons%2C%20dressed%20as%20a%20lion%2C%20in%202011.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68f697035dbc4fd10dab2d1e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221688%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author's%20husband%20trick-or-treating%20with%20their%20older%20son%2C%20dressed%20as%20a%20lion%2C%20in%202011.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Kristina%20Wright%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ce1243db-7fb8-44f6-9a44-44ee66517a5e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHalloween%20with%20little%20kids%20is%20fun%20%E2%80%94%20and%20exhausting%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20we%20had%20two%20kids%2C%20Halloween%20became%20this%20big%2C%20exciting%20holiday%20that%20somehow%20felt%20like%20it%20was%20more%20for%20me%20than%20them%20%E2%80%94%20and%20yet%20it%20was%20still%20completely%20exhausting.%20My%20oldest%20son%20was%20only%2010%20months%20old%20on%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhalloween-through-the-years-2019-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efirst%20Halloween%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20I%20think%20he%20wore%20his%20Tigger%20costume%20for%20maybe%20an%20hour%20before%20he'd%20had%20enough%20of%20the%20holiday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20following%20year%2C%20he%20was%20thrilled%20to%20wear%20his%20lion%20costume%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-trick-or-treating-halloween-2017-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ego%20trick-or-treating%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20his%208-week-old%20baby%20brother%20dressed%20as%20a%20peapod.%20It%20was%20a%20very%20early%20evening%20for%20all%20of%20us%2C%20but%20they%20were%20adorable.%20Of%20course%2C%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20claimed%20most%20of%20the%20candy%20(the%20%26quot%3Bcandy%20tax%2C%26quot%3B%20we%20called%20it)%20because%20they%20were%20too%20young%20to%20enjoy%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20time%20they%20started%20school%2C%20trick-or-treating%20had%20reached%20mythic%20proportions.%20They%20dreamed%20about%20bags%20of%20candy%20so%20big%20they%20wouldn't%20be%20able%20to%20carry%20them%20home.%20Of%20course%2C%20though%20they%20were%20full%20of%20energy%20and%20wanted%20to%20walk%20as%20far%20as%20they%20could%2C%20their%20little%20legs%20couldn't%20quite%20match%20expectations.%20My%20husband%20would%20end%20up%20carrying%20one%20or%20both%20of%20them%20while%20I%20collected%20various%20costume%20pieces%20that%20had%20fallen%20off%20or%20gotten%20too%20hot%2C%20along%20with%20their%20heavy%20bags%20of%20candy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222278%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20with%20her%20two%20kids%20on%20Halloween%2C%20sitting%20on%20the%20couch.%20The%20two%20boys%20are%20dressed%20in%20costumes.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68f6974d1c1f80efbec5ead3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222798%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20used%20to%20have%20her%20kids%20pay%20a%20%26quot%3Bcandy%20tax%26quot%3B%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20night%20on%20Halloween.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Kristina%20Wright%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d5f020dc-9b2f-494b-8e3c-683fe78bb3a0%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20middle-grade%20years%20were%20the%20sweet%20spot%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sweet%20spot%20of%20the%20trick-or-treating%20years%20for%20me%20was%20when%20my%20kids%20were%20old%20enough%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdiy-kids-halloween-costumes-parents-share-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echoose%20their%20own%20costumes%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20actually%20make%20it%20through%20two%20hours%20of%20trick-or-treating%20without%20melting%20down%20or%20asking%20to%20be%20carried%20home.%20Sure%2C%20the%20costumes%20weren't%20as%20cute%20as%20when%20they%20were%20younger%20(like%20the%20year%20they%20went%20as%20characters%20from%20a%20video%20game%20they%20were%20too%20young%20to%20play)%2C%20but%20they%20had%20a%20blast%20picking%20them%20out%20and%20happily%20trick-or-treated%20for%20as%20long%20as%20we%20would%20let%20them.%20(Which%20usually%20meant%20I%20was%20the%20one%20begging%20to%20be%20carried.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20favorite%20years%20were%20when%20their%20costumes%20and%20the%20weather%20aligned%20%E2%80%94%20neither%20too%20heavy%20when%20it%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fextreme-weather-events-nyc-whiplash-big-blizzard-snow-storm-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunseasonably%20warm%3C%2Fa%3E%20nor%20too%20lightweight%20when%20it%20was%20chilly%20or%20rainy.%20Gone%20were%20the%20days%20of%20puppies%20and%20kitties%2C%20lions%20and%20tigers%3B%20now%20they%20wanted%20to%20be%20Star%20Wars%20and%20Minecraft%20characters.%20And%20they%20had%20caught%20on%20to%20our%20candy-stealing%20ways%2C%20loudly%20declaring%20that%20the%20candy%20tax%20was%20deeply%20unfair.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c31b897c-7400-4b74-960d-716f28c56fbd%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ENow%2C%20they're%20teenagers%2C%20and%20they%20want%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20tradition%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pandemic%20stole%20one%20Halloween%20from%20us%2C%20and%20by%202021%2C%20my%20oldest%20son%20was%20almost%2012%20and%20had%20lost%20interest%20in%20trick-or-treating%2C%20while%20my%20youngest%20was%2010%20and%20thrilled%20to%20go%20as%20the%20character%20everyone%20said%20he%20looked%20like%20%E2%80%94%20Harry%20Potter.%20Since%20then%2C%20he's%20continued%20to%20be%20excited%20about%20Halloween%20even%20as%20his%20interest%20in%20formal%20costumes%20faded%2C%20cobbling%20together%20whatever%20he%20could%20find%20around%20the%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20year%20he%20was%20a%20contestant%20from%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Great%20British%20Bake%20Off%3C%2Fem%3E%20(an%20apron%2C%20a%20loaf%20of%20bread%2C%20some%20flour%20in%20his%20hair).%20Another%20year%2C%20he%20went%20as%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstarbucks-policy-crack-down-barista-notes-cups-coaching-termination-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EStarbucks%20barista%3C%2Fa%3E%20(a%20beanie%2C%20a%20Starbucks%20apron%20and%20cup%2C%20a%20headset).%20But%20now%20he's%20decided%20that%20he%2C%20too%2C%20is%20finished%20with%20trick-or-treating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221656%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author's%20kids%20dressed%20as%20a%20tiger%20and%20a%20Transformer%20in%202014.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68f69786cc993f9955d086cb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221242%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThis%20year%2C%20the%20author%20has%20realized%20how%20much%20she'll%20miss%20trick-or-treating%20with%20her%20kids.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Kristina%20Wright%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20first%20time%20in%2015%20years%2C%20I'll%20be%20handing%20out%20candy%20instead%20of%20trailing%20after%20my%20own%20costumed%20kids%20as%20they%20roam%20the%20neighborhood%20collecting%20treats.%20It'll%20be%20a%20bittersweet%20night%20%E2%80%94%20and%20yes%2C%20I%20plan%20to%20eat%20my%20feelings%20in%20fun-size%20candy%20bars.%20Because%20trick-or-treating%20is%20one%20of%20those%20childhood%20traditions%20that%20end%20far%20too%20soon.%20Like%20getting%20up%20at%20dawn%20to%20open%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdont-give-christmas-presents-to-family-friends-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChristmas%20presents%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20hiding%20a%20hundred%20Easter%20eggs%20in%20the%20yard%2C%20it%20can%20feel%20like%20more%20work%20than%20fun%20sometimes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it's%20gone%20%E2%80%94%20when%20the%20last%20costume%20has%20been%20worn%2C%20when%20the%20teens%20sleep%20in%20later%20than%20I%20do%20on%20Christmas%20morning%2C%20when%20the%20Easter%20eggs%20are%20tucked%20in%20a%20box%20in%20the%20back%20of%20the%20closet%20%E2%80%94%20all%20we're%20left%20with%20are%20the%20memories%20and%20the%20photos.%20And%20I'm%20not%20ready%20to%20be%20finished%2C%20even%20if%20they%20are.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20who%20knows%20%E2%80%94%20maybe%20in%20exchange%20for%20a%20couple%20of%20Reese's%20Peanut%20Butter%20Cups%2C%20I%20can%20lure%20my%20teens%20out%20to%20the%20porch%20to%20hand%20out%20candy%20with%20me%20and%20reminisce%20about%20their%20favorite%20Halloweens.%20After%20all%2C%20paying%20the%20candy%20tax%20has%20always%20been%20part%20of%20the%20deal%20%E2%80%94%20and%20this%20year%2C%20I'm%20more%20than%20happy%20to%20pay%20it%20for%20a%20little%20extra%20time%20with%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhalloween-kids-outgrew-trick-or-