EHe%20said%20taxing%20billionaires%20won't%20fix%20inequality%20and%20urged%20finding%20ways%20to%20help%20others%20earn%20more.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-cuban-living-like-student-set-him-up-for-success-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMark%20Cuban%3C%2Fa%3E%20says%20the%20only%20way%20to%20eliminate%20billionaires%20would%20be%20to%20destroy%20the%20stock%20market%20%E2%80%94%20and%20doing%20so%20would%20wipe%20out%20the%20savings%20of%20ordinary%20Americans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20string%20of%20posts%20on%20BlueSky%20on%20Thursday%20night%2C%20the%20billionaire%20investor%20and%20former%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-tariffs-shark-tank-playbook-manufacturing-china-mark-cuban-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EShark%20Tank%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20star%20rebuffed%20users%20who%20argued%20that%20wealth%20inequality%20could%20be%20solved%20by%20taxing%20or%20capping%20billionaires'%20wealth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECuban%20%E2%80%94%20whose%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-cuban-net-worth-2018-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%246%20billion%20fortune%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20tech%20startups%2C%20investing%2C%20and%20owning%20the%20Dallas%20Mavericks%20makes%20him%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20richest%20people%20%E2%80%94%20said%20that%20extreme%20wealth%20is%20an%20inevitable%20byproduct%20of%20the%20market%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBillionaires%20will%20exist%20as%20long%20as%20stock%20markets%20exist%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BShould%20we%20get%20rid%20of%20the%20stock%20market%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20one%20user%20said%20they'd%20like%20to%20see%20the%20market%20go%20if%20it%20meant%20preventing%20%26quot%3Bdisgusting%20examples%20of%20extreme%20wealth%2C%26quot%3B%20Cuban%20replied%3A%20%26quot%3BWhat%20should%20people%20do%20with%20the%20money%20they%20save%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20warned%20that%20dismantling%20the%20market%20would%20have%20catastrophic%20effects%20for%20everyone%2C%20not%20just%20the%20rich.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECuban%20was%20responding%20to%20another%20user%20who%20said%20that%20roughly%2090%25%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-crash-imf-risk-disorderly-corrections-valuations-global-economy-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estock%20market%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20owned%20by%20the%20richest%2010%25%20of%20US%20households%20%E2%80%94%20a%20figure%20in%20line%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-ownership-wealthiest-americans-one-percent-record-high-economy-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EFederal%20Reserve%20data%3C%2Fa%3E%20showing%20that%20the%20top%2010%25%20hold%20about%2093%25%20of%20all%20stock%20market%20wealth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20agreed%20with%20the%20statistic%20but%20argued%20that%20forcing%20those%20investors%20to%20sell%20would%20hurt%20everyone%2C%20not%20just%20the%20wealthy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAbsolutely%20true%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BBut%20that%2090%20percent%20is%20trillions%20and%20trillions%20of%20dollars%2C%20owned%20by%20everyone%20else.%20If%20you%20make%20the%20top%2010%20pct%20sell%2090%20pct%20of%20the%20market%2C%20how%20close%20to%20zero%20value%20do%20you%20think%20the%20ownership%20of%20the%2090%20percent%20goes%3F%20You%20would%20wipe%20out%20the%20savings%20of%20more%20than%20half%20the%20country.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Cuban%20argued%20that%20billionaires%20are%20a%20necessary%20byproduct%20of%20thriving%20stock%20markets%20that%20benefit%20savers%2C%20organizations%20like%20Oxfam%20and%20the%20World%20Bank%20say%20ultra-rich%20accumulations%20are%20mainly%20driven%20by%20inheritance%2C%20monopoly%20power%2C%20and%20worsen%20inequality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f280ce91-25b9-45b8-bbb7-7c1ce4bfeb7d%5C%22%3EThe%20billionaire%20tax%20debate%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECuban%20also%20argued%20that%20even%20if%20governments%20seized%20every%20dollar%20owned%20by%20billionaires%2C%20it%20wouldn't%20significantly%20improve%20public%20finances.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can%20take%20every%20penny%20that%20every%20billionaire%20has%2C%20and%20other%20than%20making%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20on%20here%20feel%20better%2C%20it%20wouldn't%20pay%20for%20the%20interest%20of%20the%20federal%20deficit%20or%20single-payer%20%5Bhealthcare%5D%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20doing%20so%20would%20probably%20tank%20the%20markets%20and%20cause%20a%20depression.%20But%20other%20than%20that%2C%20the%20rich%20would%20be%20tasty!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20Cuban%20said%20he%20would%20support%20a%20%26quot%3Bwindfall%20tax%26quot%3B%20on%20people%20earning%20%241%20billion%20or%20more%20in%20taxable%20income%20in%20a%20single%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20questioned%20the%20feasibility%20of%20wealth%20taxes%20based%20on%20stock%20valuations%2C%20asking%3A%20%26quot%3BIf%20it's%20the%20value%20of%20their%20stock%2C%20will%20you%20refund%20the%20tax%20if%20the%20stock%20market%20corrects%20or%20crashes%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22df787637-37d5-4922-a705-21acb3364d36%5C%22%3EMake%20capitalism%20fairer%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20Cuban%20offered%20a%20glimpse%20of%20what%20he%20thinks%20fairer%20capitalism%20might%20look%20like.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20a%20user%20who%20suggested%20capping%20CEO%20pay%2C%20raising%20worker%20wages%2C%20and%20changing%20laws%20so%20companies%20prioritize%20employees%20over%20shareholders%2C%20he%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20every%20employee%20should%20be%20the%20same%20percent%20of%20their%20earnings%20in%20company%20stock%20as%20the%20CEO.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20when%20another%20commenter%20suggested%20that%20public%20anger%20stems%20from%20billionaires%20acting%20selfishly%2C%20Cuban%20agreed%2