ates%20but%20that%20he%20spends%2C%20on%20average%2C%2010%20hours%20a%20week%20on%20their%20joint%20portfolio.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20partnership%20has%20kind%20of%20flourished%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Louw.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20just%20supposed%20to%20be%20this%20little%20fun%20thing%20that%20we%20do%2C%20and%20that's%20still%20what%20it%20is%2C%20but%20it's%20grown%20into%20something%20bigger%20than%20I%20think%20we%20might%20have%20both%20expected%20it%20to.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESwofford%20and%20Louw%2C%20both%2031%2C%20plan%20to%20keep%20it%20as%20a%20side%20hustle%2C%20using%20the%20cash%20flow%20to%20pay%20for%20vacations%2C%20boost%20their%20retirement%20savings%2C%20and%20contribute%20to%20their%20kids'%20future%20educations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20shared%20their%20%26quot%3Bsoftware%20stack%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20has%20allowed%20them%20to%20scale%20quickly%20without%20sacrificing%20a%20lot%20of%20their%20time.%20It%20consists%20of%20three%20AI%20tools%20and%20costs%20%2420%20a%20month.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Baselane.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWhile%20researching%20landlord%20software%20and%20business%20banking%20platforms%2C%20Swofford%20came%20across%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.baselane.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBaselane%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20offers%20both.%20It's%20an%20automated%20banking%2C%20bookkeeping%2C%20and%20rent%20collection%20tool%20that's%20become%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20their%20workflow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20the%20main%20AI%20tool%20they%20use%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20only%20one%20they%20pay%20for%20(%2420%20a%20month).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20of%20our%20rent%20collecting%20happens%20there%3B%20they%20notify%20me%20if%20someone%20has%20not%20paid%3B%20I%20check%20all%20of%20our%20expenses%20through%20there%3B%20I%20do%20all%20of%20our%20categorization%20through%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Swofford%2C%20noting%20that%20they%20also%20pay%20their%20con