20The%20houses%20pictured%20are%20located%20in%20Northern%20Virginia%20and%20are%20not%20part%20of%20Richards'%20property.%3Cp%3ENathan%20Howard%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EKay%20Richards%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Northern%20Virginia%2C%20lives%20within%20a%20mile%20radius%20of%2014%20data%20centers.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20faces%20diesel%20smells%20and%20ongoing%20buzzing%20from%20nearby%20data%20centers%2C%20but%20she%20refuses%20to%20move.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20urges%20residents%20to%20fight%20against%20data%20center%20expansion%20by%20getting%20involved%20at%20the%20local%20level.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Kay%20Richards%2C%20a%20woman%20in%20her%2060s%2C%20who%20lives%20in%20Manassas%2C%20Virginia.%20It's%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%20Business%20Insider%20reached%20out%20to%20Amazon%20for%20comment%2C%20but%20did%20not%20receive%20one%20prior%20to%20publishing.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20moved%20into%20our%20home%20over%20a%20decade%20ago%2C%20there%20were%20no%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdata-center-locations-us-map-ai-boom-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edata%20centers%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20be%20found.%20It%20was%20just%20an%20idyllic%20little%20neighborhood%20full%20of%20trees.%20It%20was%20our%20dream%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20there%20are%2014%20data%20centers%20within%20a%20mile%20radius%20of%20our%20home%2C%20belonging%20to%20various%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20constant%20buzzing%20and%20smell%20of%20what%20I%20believe%20is%20diesel%20make%20it%20hard%20for%20me%20to%20even%20go%20in%20my%20backyard.%20It's%20disheartening%20to%20see%20our%20community%20transformed%20by%20these%20industrial%20warehouses%2C%20but%20we're%20not%20going%20anywhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe'll%20continue%20to%20fight%20the%20developers%20as%20they%20