ion%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It's%20tough%20to%20say%20the%20price%20tag%20definitively%2C%20but%20being%20based%20in%20the%20largest%20US%20city%20likely%20means%20it%20comes%20with%20a%20nice%20premium.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20Jets%20are%200-7%20this%20year%20with%20a%20real%20shot%20at%20finishing%200-17%2C%20which%20would%20be%20the%20worst%20season%20in%20NFL%20history.%20They're%20tied%20with%20the%20Buffalo%20Sabres%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D7696dcf97c240f3fd9205c5d025b34f611c7c1fa5b2310de998aa9933ef79d16%26postID%3D68fa9114db84ae224e7a4f02%26postSlug%3Dnew-york-jets-nfl-private-equity-investment-please-help-2025-10%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.espn.com%252Fnfl%252Fstory%252F_%252Fid%252F42901068%252Flongest-active-postseason-droughts-nfl-mlb-nba-nhl%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20longest%20active%20playoff%20drought%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%2014%20seasons%20%E2%80%94%20across%20the%20four%20major%20US%20professional%20sports.%20(At%20least%20we're%20champs%20at%20something.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EA%20terrible%20team%20with%20a%20high%20price%20tag.%20Where%20do%20I%20sign%20up%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20also%20a%20catch.%20League%20rules%20don't%20allow%20these%20new%20investors%20to%20take%20more%20than%20a%2010%25%20stake%2C%20making%20them%20passive%20investors%20without%20voting%20power.%20(Man%2C%20I'm%20really%20doing%20a%20good%20job%20selling%20this.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20getting%20a%20foot%20in%20the%20door%20will%20give%20you%20an%20edge%20if%20the%20league%20looks%20to%20raise%20the%20limit.%20And%20if%20the%20NFL%20does%20change%20the%20rules%2C%20private-equity%20investors%20are%20known%20for%20orchestrating%20massive%20turnarounds%20(or%20at%20least%20trying%20to).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20is%20PE's%20chance.%20And%20don't%20worry%20about%20driving%20the%20team%20into%20the%20ground.%20We're%20already%20almost%20six%20feet%20under.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222b40892f-d89f-40be-8736-da58f05981b8%5C%22%3EIt's%20not%20all%20bad%20news%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Jets%20come%20with%20some%20silver%20linings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFortunately%2C%20unlike%20the%20English%20Premier%20League%2C%20the%20NFL%20doesn't%20relegate%20teams.%20So%2C%20as%20bad%20as%20the%20Jets%20are%2C%20they%20get%20to%20stay%20in%20a%20league%20that's%20minting%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20three%20guarantees%20in%20life%3A%20death%2C%20taxes%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdisney-nfl-deal-shows-who-owns-tv-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20NFL%20getting%20boatloads%20of%20money%20to%20broadcast%20its%20games%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20league%20is%20reportedly%20looking%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2025%2F09%2F24%2Fnfl-tv-rights-renegotiations-accelerated-roger-goodell.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erenegotiate%20its%20media%20deals%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20soon%20as%20next%20year%2C%20and%20it's%20bound%20to%20have%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-nfl-streaming-24-million-christmas-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elong%20list%20of%20suitors%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20money%20from%20the%20NFL's%20TV%20deals%20is%20evenly%20split%20across%20all%2032%20franchises.%20Private%20equity%20loves%20recurring%20revenue.%20How%20about%20a%20few%20hundred%20million%20dollars%20you%20can%20bank%20on%20every%20year%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJets%20fans%20are%20also%20devoted.%20They%20are%20committed.%20You%20have%20to%20be%20to%20cheer%20for%20a%20team%20like%20this.%20Looking%20for%20a%20loyal%20partner%3F%20Marry%20a%20Jets%20fan%2C%20because%20anyone%20who%20still%20roots%20for%20them%20definitely%20won't%20leave%20you.%20(My%20wife%20is%20a%20Jets%20fan%2C%20too%2C%20so%20I%20guess%20we're%20really%20stuck%20together.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20look%20at%20this%20poor%20sap%20after%20Sunday's%20loss%20to%20the%20Carolina%20Pan