ate%20massive%20chunks%20of%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20can%20get%20to%20like%20functional%20AGI%2C%26quot%3B%20Masad%20said.%20He%20defines%20functional%20AGI%20as%20AI%20that%20doesn't%20need%20human-like%20consciousness%20or%20reasoning%2C%20just%20systems%20capable%20of%20learning%20from%20real-world%20data%20and%20completing%20verifiable%20tasks%20on%20their%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe'll%20target%20every%20sector%20economy%20and%20you%20can%20automate%20a%20big%20part%20of%20labour%20that%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20on%20that%20track%20for%20sure.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMasad%20said%20he's%20not%20convinced%20that%20we'll%20ever%20reach%20true%20AGI%2C%20the%20kind%20of%20artificial%20intelligence%20that%20can%20learn%20and%20adapt%20across%20knowledge%20fields%20like%20a%20human%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20true%20AGI%20could%20%26quot%3Bpropel%20us%20to%20the%20next%20level%20of%20human%20civilization%2C%26quot%3B%20Masad%20said%20he's%20%26quot%3Bbearish%20on%20true%20AGI%20breakthrough%20because%20what%20we%20built%20is%20so%20useful%20and%20economically%20valuable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMasad%20also%20said%20the%20industry%20might%20be%20stuck%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Blocal%20maximum%20trap%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20means%20AI%20companies%20are%20optimizing%20what%20already%20works%20instead%20of%20reinventing%20the%20field.%20By%20chasing%20small%2C%20profitable%20improvements%20to%20today's%20large%20models%2C%20they%20could%20be%20missing%20the%20path%20to%20a%20true%20breakthrough.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMaybe%20the%20general%20problem%20is%20actually%20not%20within%20our%20lifetimes%2C%26quot%3B%20Masad%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20solving%20the%20problem%20of%20general%20intelligence%20itself.%20%26quot%3BWho%20knows%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMasad%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2261beb806-a789-436d-b