%20Manchurian%2C%20cashew%20sprouts%20butter%20%3Cem%3Emasala%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20cashew%20sprouts%20%3Cem%3Emalai%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20cashew%20sprouts%20schezwan%2C%20cashew%20sprouts%20Malabar%20%3Cem%3Emasala%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20cashew%20sprouts%20%3Cem%3Etheyal%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20cashew%20sprouts%20soup%20premix%2C%20cashew%20sprouts%20brine%2C%20pickles%2C%20and%20fresh%20cashew%20sprouts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20meticulous%20focus%20on%20quality%20and%20value%2C%20Brijith%20priced%20his%20sprouted%20cashews%20at%20Rs%201%2C000%20per%20kg.%20Through%20strategic%20partnerships%20with%20celebrity%20chefs%2C%20star%20hotels%2C%20and%20catering%20groups%2C%20Brijith%20positioned%20his%20premium%20cashew%20sprout%20products%20in%20a%20niche%20market%20segment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20his%20regular%20customers%20Thomas%2C%20who%20works%20as%20a%20corporate%20chef%20at%20Paragon%20group%20of%20restaurants%2C%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20experienced%20these%20cashew%20sprouts%20can%20be%20included%20in%20a%20healthy%20diet%20and%20lots%20of%20various%20dishes%20can%20be%20prepared%20with%20adaptability.%20It%20is%20not%20easily%20available%20in%20stores%20so%20people%20have%20some%20curiosity%20about%20it.%20These%20dishes%20are%20repeatedly%20demanded%20from%20our%20happy%20customers%20at%20the%20restaurant.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20unique%20positioning%20in%20the%20market%20enabled%20Brijith%20to%20secure%20a%20steady%20clientele%20and%20achieve%20a%20turnover%20of%20Rs%2025%20lakh%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20his%20endeavours%20were%20not%20only%20driven%20by%20a%20passion%20for%20innovation%20but%20also%20by%20a%20commitment%20to%20empower%20local%20farmers.%20By%20purchasing%20wet%20cashews%20from%20at%20least%2011%20local%20farmers%2C%20Brijith%20managed%20to%20provide%20a%20sustainable%20solution%20by%20transforming%20them%20into%20high-quality%20sprouted%20cashews.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBy%20reimagining%20traditional%20practi